recordedBy: Fritsch, PW; Barbosa, E; Aranha, JLM
locality: Trail to Pico Caratuva, ca. 4 km from Fazenda Pico Paraná. The Fazenda is ca. 5 km from BR-160
occurrenceRemarks: Cloud forest above Mata Atlântica, granite base rock. Tree 10 m tall with spreading, rounded crown. Corolla green, filaments white. Other individuals in the area are shrubs. Abundant along trail

recordedBy: Fritsch, PW; Barbosa, E; Aranha, JLM
locality: Along a trail on W slope of Morro Canal. Entrance to the trail is along a road ca. 12 km from BR-277 (the turnoff from BR-277 is ca. 500 m before Polícia Rodoviária Federal). Serra do Mar
occurrenceRemarks: Elfin cloud forest. Shrub or small tree to 3 m tall. Corolla greenish white; young fruit green. Occasional on windswept slope

recordedBy: Almeda, F; Martins, AB; Fritsch, PW; Aranha, JLM; Bush, C; Belinello, R
locality: Road from Garganta do Registro to Abrigo Rebouças and Parque Nacional do Itatiaia between Km 6 and Km 13.&nf;Campo de altitude vegetation.
occurrenceRemarks: Tree 5 m tall. Young fruits green. Mature fruits purplish black. Occasional.

recordedBy: J. M. A. Braga; et al
locality: Parque Nacional do Itatiaia. Planalto, Agulhas Negras, via tradicional para o cume
occurrenceRemarks: Na encosta íngrime entre a vegetação arbustiva no encrave. Arbusto, 1,5m de alt., heliófilo. Folhas cartáceas. Flores verdes, estames alvos amarelados
